          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "Step 1",
            "heading": "<strong>Shop Smart</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Browse thousands of premium toys, from first rattles to rocket-building kits. Choose <strong>Brand New</strong> or go for <strong>Certified Refurbished - </strong>same joy, kinder price, way less landfill. Filter by your kid’s age, the skills you want to sneak in this month. And because we price-match across Amazon, Flipkart, and the big guys — you’re never overpaying.</p>",
            "button_label": "Browse the Catalogue",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/all",
            "top_space": ""
          }
        },
        "row_Et6P4f": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "STEP 2",
            "heading": "<strong>Play your heart out.</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Your toy lands at your doorstep. And then? It’s yours. Fully. Properly. Forever-if-you-want-it yours. No rental meter ticking. No “please return by Friday” emails. No pressure. Play with it for three weeks or three years - the only clock that matters is your kid’s obsession timeline.</p>",
            "button_label": "Shop by Age",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections",
            "top_space": ""
          }
        },
        "row_mtMeNQ": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "Step 3",
            "heading": "Done? We’ll Come Get It",
            "text": "<p>One day - probably sooner than you think the toy stops being <strong>the</strong> toy. That’s your cue. Open the app, tap <strong>Schedule a pickup </strong>done. Our team swings by, runs a quick quality check, and boom - you get a <strong>flat 60% back</strong>. Straight to your original payment method, or as EleFant credit (which unlocks a little bonus because we like repeat customers).</p>",
            "button_label": "Schedule a Pickup",
            "button_link": "",
            "top_space": ""
          }
        }
      },
